}, {
  "@id" : "https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR",
  "@type" : [ "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual" ],
  "http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type" : [ {
    "@id" : "https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label" : [ {
    "@language" : "el",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "fr",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "it",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "no",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "pt",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "ro",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response"
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition" : [ {
    "@language" : "no",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) er et åtteårig prosjekt finansiert av ANR.\n\n                           MARMOR-prosjektet har to mål:\n\n                           å strukturere det franske vitenskapelige miljøet ved å gi forskningsinfrastrukturen Epos-France (tidligere Résif) utstyret som trengs for å gjennomføre forskning på høyt nivå med bruk av undervannsseismologi og geodesiverktøy,\n\n                           å etablere en undervanns observasjonsinfrastruktur på Mayotte for å sikre kontinuerlig, sanntids og døgnkontinuerlig seismologisk overvåking, samt støtte tverrfaglig forskning på fenomenene knyttet til den pågående seismo-vulkanske krisen."
  }, {
    "@language" : "es",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) es un proyecto de ocho años financiado por la ANR.\n\n                           El proyecto MARMOR tiene un doble objetivo:\n\n                           estructurar la comunidad científica francesa proporcionando a la infraestructura de investigación Epos-France (antes Résif) el equipamiento necesario para llevar a cabo investigaciones de excelencia utilizando herramientas de sismología y geodesia submarinas,\n\n                           poner en marcha una infraestructura de observación submarina en Mayotte para garantizar la vigilancia sismológica continua, en tiempo real y 24/7, y desarrollar investigaciones multidisciplinares sobre los fenómenos asociados a la crisis sismo-volcánica en curso."
  }, {
    "@language" : "fr",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) est un projet d’une durée de huit ans financé par l’ANR.\n\n                           Le projet MARMOR a un double objectif :\n\n                           structurer la communauté scientifique française en fournissant à l’infrastructure de recherche Epos-France (anciennement Résif) les équipements nécessaires pour conduire des recherches d’excellence utilisant les outils de la sismologie et de la géodésie sous-marines,\n\n                           mettre en place une infrastructure d’observation sous-marine à Mayotte afin d’assurer une surveillance sismologique continue, en temps réel et 24/7, et de conduire des recherches multidisciplinaires sur les phénomènes associés à la crise sismo-volcanique en cours."
  }, {
    "@language" : "ro",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) este un proiect cu durata de opt ani finanțat de ANR.\n\n                           Proiectul MARMOR are un dublu obiectiv:\n\n                           să structureze comunitatea științifică franceză, furnizând infrastructurii de cercetare Epos-France (fost Résif) echipamentele necesare pentru desfășurarea unor cercetări de excelență folosind instrumente de seismologie și geodezie submarine,\n\n                           să implementeze o infrastructură de observare submarină în Mayotte pentru a asigura monitorizarea seismologică continuă, în timp real și 24/7, precum și pentru a sprijini cercetarea multidisciplinară asupra fenomenelor asociate crizei seismo-vulcanice în curs."
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) is an eight-year project funded by the ANR.\n                           \n                           The MARMOR project has two objectives:\n                           \n                           to structure the French scientific community by providing the Epos-France research infrastructure (formerly Résif) with the equipment required to conduct high-level research using submarine seismology and geodesy tools,\n\n                           to establish an underwater observation infrastructure in Mayotte in order to ensure continuous, real-time, 24/7 seismological monitoring and to support multidisciplinary research on the phenomena associated with the ongoing seismo-volcanic crisis."
  }, {
    "@language" : "it",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) è un progetto della durata di otto anni finanziato dall’ANR.\n\n                           Il progetto MARMOR ha un duplice obiettivo:\n\n                           strutturare la comunità scientifica francese fornendo all’infrastruttura di ricerca Epos-France (precedentemente Résif) le attrezzature necessarie per svolgere ricerche di eccellenza utilizzando strumenti di sismologia e geodesia sottomarina,\n\n                           realizzare un’infrastruttura di osservazione sottomarina a Mayotte per garantire una sorveglianza sismologica continua, in tempo reale e 24/7, e sostenere ricerche multidisciplinari sui fenomeni associati alla crisi sismo-vulcanica in corso."
  }, {
    "@language" : "pt",
    "@value" : "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) é um projeto com duração de oito anos financiado pela ANR.\n\n                           O projeto MARMOR tem um duplo objetivo:\n\n                           estruturar a comunidade científica francesa, fornecendo à infraestrutura de investigação Epos-France (anteriormente Résif) os equipamentos necessários para realizar investigação de excelência com recurso a ferramentas de sismologia e geodesia submarinas,\n\n                           instalar uma infraestrutura de observação submarina em Mayotte para assegurar uma vigilância sismológica contínua, em tempo real e 24/7, e apoiar investigação multidisciplinar sobre os fenómenos associados à crise sismo-vulcânica em curso."
  }, {
    "@language" : "el",
    "@value" : "Το MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) είναι ένα οκταετές έργο που χρηματοδοτείται από την ANR.\n                           \n                           Το έργο MARMOR έχει διπλό στόχο:\n                           \n                           να δομήσει τη γαλλική επιστημονική κοινότητα, παρέχοντας στην ερευνητική υποδομή Epos-France (πρώην Résif) τον απαραίτητο εξοπλισμό για την ανάπτυξη ερευνητικής αριστείας με χρήση εργαλείων υποθαλάσσιας σεισμολογίας και γεωδαισίας,\n                           \n                           να εγκαταστήσει μια υποθαλάσσια υποδομή παρατήρησης στη Μαγιότ, ώστε να καλύπτει τις ανάγκες συνεχούς, σε πραγματικό χρόνο και 24/7 σεισμολογικής επιτήρησης και να υποστηρίζει διεπιστημονική έρευνα για τα φαινόμενα που σχετίζονται με την εν εξελίξει σεισμοηφαιστειακή κρίση."
  } ],
  "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel" : [ {
    "@language" : "el",
    "@value" : "MARMOR"
  }, {
    "@language" : "en",
